{"tid":154931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威慘忍捕鯨 合法獵殺母鯨「一屍兩命」","createTime":"2017-03-13T15:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T16:56:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4fb9a66d57509866a7f617fa32b59f3353080d","tid":154931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1999166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1999166&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a646ebdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1999166&h=26ba1818\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1999166</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpf8KkIG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpf8KkIG.jpg&h=8e20d0b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">挪威紀錄片揭示，被捕獲的母鯨中有逾9成懷有身孕。（歐新社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本捕殺海豚的陋習為人詬病外，挪威也因合法獵殺鯨魚而遭到動物權益保護者大力譴責，挪威有線電視台日前播出紀錄片，當地大批母鯨遭到殺害，最殘忍的是，被捕獲的母鯨中，近90%都已經懷孕，腹中的胎兒遭到強行取出，即使遭到強烈抨擊，但有船長仍不以為意說：「母鯨懷孕代表牠們身體健康」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTdF0bE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTdF0bE.jpg&h=1895b4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">挪威紀錄片揭示，大量母鯨腹中胎兒被強行取出的畫面，遭到動保團體強力譴責。（法新社）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，挪威廣播公司（NRK）製作捕鯨紀錄片，片中船員將獵捕的小鬚鯨抬上船後，便開始進行宰割作業，更讓人無法接受的是，逾9成都是母鯨，且「幾乎全數懷孕」，媽媽被殺後，腹中的胎兒也遭到強行取出，瑞士動物權利組織OceanCare強力譴責：「捕鯨者不僅僅是獵殺這些鯨魚，連牠們的下一代也不放過」，一名捕鯨船船長道格（Dag Myklebust）則認為，絕大多數的動物被送進屠宰場時，也懷有身孕，這是一種很自然的現象，且母鯨順利懷孕代表牠們本身非常健康。<br />\n儘管挪威綠色和平的負責人吉洛森（Truls Gulowsen）認為挪威捕鯨的現狀令人難以接受，違反國際社會禁止捕鯨的共識，但捕鯨在挪威仍屬合法行為。<br />\n1986年，挪威、日本、冰島三國拒絕加入國際聯合禁捕鯨魚的約束，挪威漁業部長在數周前宣布，將2017的補經限額增至999頭，比在2016年的額度多了199頭。在未來或提升至2000頭並希望能開發歐洲市場，但因鯨魚買賣買賣在歐洲仍不合法，因此挪威宰殺的鯨魚多半輸出至日本。"},{"pid":"c7dd68a3870a94de51b1d08353478e35207b89ea","tid":154931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466b8602c93efcc01706dfe2f3d74853e2a9ad92","tid":154931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049d0ef0952e15cb3cf3c5fc905955be28e2a73a","tid":154931,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"在商業世界勞役／折磨同類<br />\n卻口口聲聲維護大自然其他物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952bd5ba559ab894efcb7e733c26d92b6fa286dc","tid":154931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac6085f927f6b58ee3ac9bcdcfd81a367ebd49b","tid":154931,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"其實日本真係食到咁多鯨魚？"},{"pid":"b735ebe45a177e337072092681534bda8c43dabc","tid":154931,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>殘忍呀</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\nBTW,點睇得出殘忍?"},{"pid":"894ba6d91e3fc6bbb502245144e9b3624f6ea808","tid":154931,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11534128dd59fdb6db245e874280c1354934ee05","tid":154931,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"吃鯨魚的人"},{"pid":"40ac0d2729f82e80c52189d39d124a27839fa46d","tid":154931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺鯨方式係人道既話其實冇咩大問題，生意要長做長有我估人類唔會捕到佢絕種為止既，其他動物一樣，冇咩好反，除左貓狗係特別d，同人類之間有特別既情感係度，人唔人道都唔應該殺</blockquote><br />\n你明唔明白就係因為鯨魚就嚟絕種先要禁架?唔係咩大愛啊"},{"pid":"08341d0d22a3047f5ac61b3a060d19b8ceef366f","tid":154931,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋咩殘忍<br />\n新聞用咁biased 既topic 都冇問題?"},{"pid":"d58352126e160c4e096cea68a2ce9d89466c8fc7","tid":154931,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}